				autem eaque tenetur tempore? Atque totam et quam quo deleniti voluptas laudantium.
				Mollitia id quaerat odio, nulla animi at molestias?
			</h2>
			<h2>
				Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Molestiae perspiciatis
				autem eaque tenetur tempore? Atque totam et quam quo deleniti voluptas laudantium.
				Mollitia id quaerat odio, nulla animi at molestias?
			</h2>
		</Section.SideContent>

		<div class="col-span-full lg:col-start-2">
			<p class="text-balance text-4xl">
				Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Molestiae perspiciatis
				autem eaque tenetur tempore? Atque totam et quam quo deleniti voluptas laudantium.
				Mollitia id quaerat odio, nulla animi at molestias?
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class={cx(subgrid())}>
			<div class={"relative col-span-full hidden grid-cols-subgrid md:grid"}>
				<div class="hidden h-14 w-full lg:col-[1/span_1] lg:block"></div>
				<div class="col-[1/span_2] lg:col-[2/span_5]">Focus</div>
				<div class="col-[3/span_2] lg:col-[7/span_5]">Experience</div>
				<Separator class="lg:col-start-1" fullScreen />
			</div>

			<div
				class={cx(
					vstack(),
					"col-[1/span_2] lg:col-[2/span_5] text-2xl gap-4 font-medium mb-32 lg:mb-0",
				)}
			>
				<div class="w-full md:hidden">
					<div class="text-base font-normal">Focus</div>
					<Separator fullScreen />
				</div>

				<p class="mt-6 lg:mt-0">Web development</p>
				<p>Backend development</p>
				<p>Distributed systems</p>
				<p>Performance</p>
				<p>Reliability</p>
				<p>Extensiveness</p>
				<p>Ease of use</p>
				<p>User experience</p>
			</div>

			<div class="col-[3/span_2] grid gap-8 lg:col-[7/span_5] lg:grid-cols-2">
				<div class="col-span-full w-full md:hidden">
					<div class="text-base font-normal">Experience</div>
					<Separator fullScreen />
				</div>

				<WorkCard
					name="Upriver Technologies"
					period={{ start: new Date("2021-12"), end: new Date("2023-06") }}
					subtitle="Created web and native apps for several startups"
					class="mt-6 lg:mt-0"
				/>
